The report on household budgets published on Friday by the Central Statistical Office shows that last year they assessed their financial situation as good or rather good. as much as 44 percent of them.
A year earlier, this percentage was 37.2 percent, in 2016 it was 33.5 percent, and earlier - since 2009, when the statistical office examined subjective assessments of the situation of households for the first time - it never exceeded 30 percent.
